<div id="BasePoints" class="collapse in">

		<p>Base-Points represent the base "skill" of a player, and are calculated from values at their DotaBuff profile. This means that playing public matchmaking can affect your Base-Points. Here is the formula for the calculation:
</p>
<strong>Base-Points</strong> = totalGames/10(rounded up) + Wins/10(rounded up) + WinRate-50 * 10(rounded up)

